uote><blockquote><blockquote>小學宿營一定有呢味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食到有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲汁好似藥水咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係用d即開即用吉士粉，加d檸檬汁整</blockquote><br />\n想知吉士粉邊到買，去親惠康都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩可以代替吉士粉？</blockquote><br />\n烘焙店都有架啦，個d叫即用吉士粉，加水開就得。代替就係用蛋黃煮，不過就唔會點用係西檸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f262e6cf9735ecaa0e6a96da911d9b9d3e740833","tid":439072,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:24:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得世上最難食既就係西檸雞,古老肉, 糖醋魚果類食物"},{"pid":"9f0c6d96c51168da8090d79d536a80a96b8217aa","tid":439072,"uid":66557,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:26:32.000Z","msg":"最撚憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大部份揾生果類煮既餸都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cdf6745bebe3d71686cccf84a0b3be94a50501","tid":439072,"uid":60015,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:26:54.000Z","msg":"真係好撚難食<br />\n但偏偏次撚次食飯都有人叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩件事完全唔撚啱<br />\n又咸又酸又甜咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有咁撚多小朋友話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7efb2bbce23a1a6651182ddb10faebeb67a1e0","tid":439072,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:29:30.000Z","msg":"見到想食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b40f4175c6afba68b0428e9ee16dd97264a4f2e","tid":439072,"uid":66557,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係好撚難食<br />\n但偏偏次撚次食飯都有人叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩件事完全唔撚啱<br />\n又咸又酸又甜咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有咁撚多小朋友話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲諗撚住入嚟一齊屌西檸雞，點知個個話正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cac31a6e8a7f59ad27bbbdc930510ce294eafb0","tid":439072,"uid":72054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到想食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09491d38b34aaeb74934f8e1648b7c69432010d","tid":439072,"uid":122155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:30:12.000Z","msg":"西檸雞真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說上年我去法國貝桑松學法文 <br />\n貝桑松有間越南人開嘅中越餐館 <br />\n我見有一味中文解做檸檬雞嘅餸<br />\n我以為係西檸雞 所以就嗌左<br />\n點知係西檸雞丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77dcdc4c5d74895539f413c2059ecc2d4f3003ad","tid":439072,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"陳根記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a7cf7b975d171d64e79f5cdc249d77dffb2397","tid":439072,"uid":107147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"紅磡梁忠記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2521fec437b8900c41f1228b7ec9f9fc6437845c","tid":439072,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:33:52.000Z","m