normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好開胃<br />\n<br />\n有冇手足有好推介去邊食最高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/211530_7693b1d2c14a4e806d20ca59cc7b7d76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F211530_7693b1d2c14a4e806d20ca59cc7b7d76.jpg&h=74f0560c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己煮最撚好食</blockquote><br />\n煮野食白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做我男朋友 我煮比你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喂喂我單身啊，18歲卜卜脆"},{"pid":"936d78673c5b9d997f8ba87657d9c71bc704cbcf","tid":439072,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:24:54.000Z","msg":"未食過好味既<br />\n唔可以話好食我覺得<br />\n只係一種將又&quot;UN&quot;又唔好食既隔夜雞肉再煮一味野出黎"},{"pid":"5bb41f993bf05acb64fbd6e21b4f85a37223273d","tid":439072,"uid":55792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"口水分泌突發增加"},{"pid":"a226a86e7ba45d99ec98e1b567947799da20c656","tid":439072,"uid":99573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:27:23.000Z","msg":"長沙灣<br />\n美食城"},{"pid":"e0112bac8fc9570efe6c8d93873de6fd817c7e47","tid":439072,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"Shining雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254df4e43e120f2debccd6d6e70852402febd1a8","tid":439072,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:41:32.000Z","msg":"必食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ed72d3605c90ba35dd8ea523c09552766a57e1","tid":439072,"uid":24035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:52:34.000Z","msg":"好撚睇廚師手藝<br />\n之前食過  屌你有檸檬洗潔精味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63510d3c37f5707ae93f793540878c2e0f25d189","tid":439072,"uid":43095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>西檸雞係最好拎黎清 過期雞 既煮法<br />\n<br />\n又炸又酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當舊肉開始變味<br />\n攞濃味醬汁醃左佢拎去煮就冇晒味<br />\n<br />\n中式廚房就係 生炒骨 沙拉骨 西檸雞 水煮牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沙拉骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59ccce0d7b136c2ed9b0c243a1b0bd2607f2a59","tid":439072,"uid":149485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九龍城 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樂富 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食過咁多間呢兩間係最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔撚係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔識欣賞 呢兩間大把野好食過佢個西檸雞呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569e455cb3d4d46ed6a34ed9509f09a6fa46a410","tid":439072,"uid":13883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T19:02:44.000Z","msg":"樂富聯合興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" c